zsa zsa zsu.t: Comes from "Sex and the City", where Carrie describes it as the feeling you get when you meet someone you really really like. That sort of lovey, butterflies feeling when you just want to be with someone.\n> Carrie: I met this new guy Berger, and I just get that zsa zsa zsu.\n
